title: Top 10 3DS Eshop Games! -- New and Improved! -- The Branman
description:
New look, same great taste!
...That is, if videos even had a taste. My old 3DS Eshop videos were hot garbage, but somehow they're the most popular here on the channel. I owe it to you guys to provide that video you like so much with the added quality I've begun to develop since then. This has gotta be my longest video yet, so enjoy!

Also, don't forget to leave a comment with your favorite 3DS Download title! I've loved reading ya'll's comments on the previous videos about your favorites. And of course, if you have any recommendations for me, let me know! I've been playing my 3DS more lately :D
